title: Bug 7752: Export multiple files with same file name under different directories to zip file fails.
description:
Steps to reproduce:
1. Launch WSWB and create two projects.

OB: No details provided.
EB: When exporting the files with the same name but under different directories to a zip file, the export fails and an error message is displayed.
SR: 
2. Under each project, create a new file with the same name (such as "foo.txt").
3. From the main menu, select File>Export and choose the option to export as Zip File.
4. Attempt to export the files.
